headline: Equifax: After Years Of Depressed Mortgage Activity, The Situation Might Change Soon
summary: Equifax stands to gain from a housing recovery, lower rates, and potential policy shifts, boosting mortgage-driven revenue. See why EFX stock is a strong buy.
